  "page": "Sylvenna Sand",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Sylvenna Sand</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Essie,_Sylvenna_Sand,_and_Gaemon_Palehair_by_Riotarttherite.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Essie, Sylvenna Sand, and Gaemon Palehair by Riotarttherite.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/ba/Essie%2C_Sylvenna_Sand%2C_and_Gaemon_Palehair_by_Riotarttherite.png/350px-Essie%2C_Sylvenna_Sand%2C_and_Gaemon_Palehair_by_Riotarttherite.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"408\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/ba/Essie%2C_Sylvenna_Sand%2C_and_Gaemon_Palehair_by_Riotarttherite.png/525px-Essie%2C_Sylvenna_Sand%2C_and_Gaemon_Palehair_by_Riotarttherite.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/ba/Essie%2C_Sylvenna_Sand%2C_and_Gaemon_Palehair_by_Riotarttherite.png/700px-Essie%2C_Sylvenna_Sand%2C_and_Gaemon_Palehair_by_Riotarttherite.png 2x\" /></a><div>From left to right, <a href=\"/index.php/Gaemon_Palehair\" title=\"Gaemon Palehair\">Gaemon Palehair</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Essie\" title=\"Essie\">Essie</a>, and Sylvenna, by Riotarttherite ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Kisses\" title=\"House of Kisses\">House of Kisses</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Gaemon_Palehair\" title=\"Gaemon Palehair\">Gaemon Palehair</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Lover</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Essie\" title=\"Essie\">Essie</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Sylvenna Sand</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> and a <a href=\"/index.php/Whore\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Whore\">whore</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Kisses\" title=\"House of Kisses\">House of Kisses</a>, a brothel in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sylvenna_Sand&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Sylvenna was the <a href=\"/index.php/Paramour\" title=\"Paramour\">paramour</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Essie\" title=\"Essie\">Essie</a>, another whore and the mother of <a href=\"/index.php/Gaemon_Palehair\" title=\"Gaemon Palehair\">Gaemon Palehair</a>, a pretender king during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>. Gaemon was claimed to be a <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_queer_customs_of_the_south.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_queer_customs_of_the_south.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_of_the_Three_Kings\" title=\"Moon of the Three Kings\">Moon of the Three Kings</a>, after <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a>'s escape from <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, Gaemon gathered thousands of followers and issued a series of edicts, quite likely the work of Sylvenna, for some of them reflected the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynar\" title=\"Rhoynar\">Rhoynish</a> views on women inherited by the <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dornish\">Dornish</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_queer_customs_of_the_south.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_queer_customs_of_the_south.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After the city was taken by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Borros_Baratheon\" title=\"Borros Baratheon\">Borros Baratheon</a> in Aegon II's name, Sylvenna was arrested alongside \"King\" Gaemon, Essie, and the rest of his \"court\". After Aegon's return to the capital, Sylvenna was hanged from the battlements of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> alongside Essie and twenty seven followers of the false king.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_short.2C_sad_reign_of_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_short.2C_sad_reign_of_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sylvenna_Sand&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Targaryen Kings: Aegon II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_queer_customs_of_the_south.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_queer_customs_of_the_south.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_queer_customs_of_the_south.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Dorne: Queer Customs of the South.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_short.2C_sad_reign_of_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_short.2C_sad_reign_of_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - The Short, Sad Reign of Aegon II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404045607\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.079 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.273 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 780/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10563/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7129/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2023/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2706/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.65 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  259.919      1 -total\n 96.30%  250.307      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 95.86%  249.166      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.13%   31.532     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.38%   11.380      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  4.18%   10.868      5 Template:Ref\n  2.42%    6.300      5 Template:Ref/core\n  1.76%    4.577      1 Template:Date\n  1.06%    2.744      1 Template:References\n  0.40%    1.052      2 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaf